# bat configuration
#
# Theme follows the terminal's light/dark background, matching Ghostty
# (light = One Half Light, dark = Ayu). bat detects the background color (OSC 11)
# and picks --theme-light or --theme-dark automatically, so no shell wiring is
# needed. The dark theme "ayu-dark" is the custom bat theme in themes/, registered
# by `bat cache --build` (see .chezmoiscripts/run_onchange_after_build-bat-cache).
--theme="auto"
--theme-light="OneHalfLight"
--theme-dark="ayu-dark"
